      "writtenOn": "2026-04-01T03:47:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "?  The bug is in the above config.  You shouldn\u0027t be probing on Decorator.Asset interfaces.  I\u0027m not against this change, but ultimately the bad config is the problem.  You should be probing on the specific API, not an asset API.",
      "parentUuid": "64e81994_a203494f",
      "revId": "ef5d49f761609c4b28ba4327c2a7342cba47a474",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
