      "message": "@alexander.hansen@9elements.com Exactly. Changing the probe was an idea that I had too, but haven\u0027t looked too much into. will check it.\n\n\n@ed@tanous.net `devicetree-vpd-parser` exports the values on the `Decorator.Asset` interface [1], which is also defined in the design doc [2]. Another way to solve the issue would be either:\n- allowing to filter by D-Bus names in the Probe, or\n\n- move the properties from `devicetree-vpd-parser` into another interface, which in the end would require a change in the design.\n\n[1] https://github.com/openbmc/entity-manager/blob/d40558216ad85e99f3c37614fc96e088241a4f72/src/devicetree_vpd_parser/machine_context.hpp#L10-L16\n[2] https://github.com/openbmc/docs/blob/49beca34959cb2922a0dede07da9ec52dc4f4be5/designs/entity-manager-hw-id-vpd-discover-via-device-tree.md?plain\u003d1#L315-L325",
      "parentUuid": "175c84b9_c3b2a8f0",
      "revId": "ef5d49f761609c4b28ba4327c2a7342cba47a474",
